data.description: This spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome, located minutes from Stone Mountain Park offers an open living concept and modern finishes. Built in 2020, this townhouse has hardwoods on the main level and staircase, a kitchen island with granite countertops perfect for entertaining and 42" cabinets.  A spacious master bedroom with tray ceilings, dual vanities and a walk-in closet is the ultimate owners suite. Two spacious bedrooms are absolutely perfect for a beautiful nursery, home office/gym, or guest bedroom.  The fenced backyard is a great spot to grill and entertain family and friends. Conveniently located, this townhome is only 25 minutes from Downtown Atlanta, and is within minutes of multiple shopping plazas and entertainment options. It's the ideal starter home!
